  <summary>9/21/2001--Introduced.
Prohibits an air carrier that receives Federal relief funds as a result of the terrorist attacks of September 11, 2001, from using such funds to increase the total amount of compensation received by a top executive of the carrier in calendar year 2000.</summary>
